description.p:
(a) providing a cell line which expresses urokinase-type plasminogen activator (u-PA);


(b) providing an expression vector comprising a nucleotide sequence encoding for a Gs or Gq protein coupled receptor, said receptor not normally expressed in said cell line of step (a);


(c) introducing said expression vector into said cell line, thereby providing stably transfected cells;


(d) contacting said stably transfected cells with said compound of interest; and


(e) measuring the u-PA activity of the cell culture supernatant of said cells of step (d).
